What it took to get this working on windows

Step 1: Download and unzip libusb: https://sourceforge.net/projects/libusb-win32/

Step 2: Copy libusb-win32-bin-*/bin/x86/libusb0.dll to c:\windows\syswow32\libusb0.dll

Step 3: Install driver for device by going to device manager, open atmega device, update driver, point it at the dfu-programmer directory.

Step 4: Flash away!
